## Verdict

Reliability improved:

- Native app polling can now be tested with one committed command.
- The diagnostic proves Pentagon.app is running and contains the native trigger hook surface.
- The diagnostic proves the native app did not claim or complete the probe while the bridge was stopped.
- The diagnostic avoids false positive log counts from its own log predicate.

Still not complete:

Native Pentagon handoff activation remains red. This is stronger diagnosis, not full goal completion.
